snippet.title: Coppermine Photo Gallery
snippet.description: Coppermine is an easily set-up, fast, feature-rich photo gallery script with mySQL database, user management, private galleries, automatic thumbnail creation, ecard feature and a template system for easy customization to match the rest of a site.

snippet.title: JMG Photo Printer
snippet.description: A program for printing and editing pictures. Pictures for printing are selected with checkboxes. So you don't have to have a hassle with the mouse and the keyboard to select pictures and you can select pictures from multiple folders. Together with ufraw-batch RAW pictures are shown and can be converted to jpg. If you want to organize your pictures you can do this in the database treeview.

snippet.title: JBoss photo rating website
snippet.description: A photo uploading and rating website written using Java 1.5 to run on JBoss 4.2.2 and MySQL, on Windows XP. Defaults to Linux if not on Windows XP, this can be altered in the code as required. Makes use of the sourceforge project http://skewpassim.sourceforge.net
